des: This is a tri-daily podcast that covers the latest in news across Geelong, The Surf Coast, Bellarine Peninsula and Wyndham Vale. Using the combined newsroom and journalists from Bay 93.9 and K Rock 95.5, this podcast is unrivaled in providing the latest, most comprehensive and accurate news, trusted by Geelong.
